00:27:10,270 --> 00:27:11,240
My another job:

608
00:27:11,310 --> 00:27:12,680
newspaper correspondent.

609
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:14,880
The travel rush is
the hottest topic now.

610
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:16,160
I wanna write a feature

611
00:27:16,270 --> 00:27:17,720
from the perspective

612
00:27:17,830 --> 00:27:18,510
of workers here.

613
00:27:21,270 --> 00:27:22,240
Anything else?

614
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:24,070
Ever been a lawyer?

615
00:27:27,070 --> 00:27:28,720
I majored in law.

616
00:27:30,480 --> 00:27:31,790
Really?

617
00:27:31,960 --> 00:27:33,440
Of course.

618
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:36,920
Help me with a lawsuit.

619
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:38,440
Win it, and I'll pay you.

620
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:41,680
Suing who?

621
00:27:50,070 --> 00:27:51,960
What are you doing?

622
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:53,310
No work today.

623
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,680
Why set an alarm?

624
00:27:54,830 --> 00:27:55,790
So annoying!

625
00:27:56,070 --> 00:27:56,920
Where's Wanzhi?

626
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:04,270
Where did she go?

627
00:28:05,240 --> 00:28:06,790
See if her luggage is here.

628
00:28:07,070 --> 00:28:08,510
Hope she didn't already leave.

629
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:09,440
She still owes you

630
00:28:09,480 --> 00:28:10,350
1,000.

631
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:11,680
What are you saying?

632
00:28:11,750 --> 00:28:12,680
After all this time,

633
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:13,880
you still don't know her?

634
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:15,680
Just kidding.

635
00:28:22,310 --> 00:28:23,960
Haven't even talked to them yet,

636
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:25,270
and you want to sue?

637
00:28:25,920 --> 00:28:27,000
When you were job hunting,

638
00:28:27,030 --> 00:28:27,960
it was very tough.

639
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:29,310
They gave you a shot.

640
00:28:29,750 --> 00:28:31,200
You should be grateful.

641
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:32,720
Who says I'm not?

642
00:28:33,110 --> 00:28:34,160
That's a different matter.

643
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:36,440
The bonus was promised from the start.

644
00:28:37,030 --> 00:28:38,510
But you don't have a contract.

645
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:40,400
Verbal agreements are legally binding.

646
00:28:40,750 --> 00:28:41,680
Useless education.

647
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:43,920
I know.

648
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:45,550
But that's complicated.

649
00:28:45,920 --> 00:28:47,310
I'm not sure whether the court

650
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:48,000
will hear it.

651
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:48,640
Besides,

652
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:49,880
you have to wait in line.

653
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:51,790
The court will gather evidence.

654
00:28:52,030 --> 00:28:53,590
But workers don't stay long there.

655
00:28:53,920 --> 00:28:54,720
You may not be able

656
00:28:54,790 --> 00:28:55,960
to find the witnesses.

657
00:28:57,270 --> 00:28:58,830
This case would be a real grind

658
00:28:59,110 --> 00:29:00,550
for any lawyer.

659
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:02,830
And there's not much money in it.

660
00:29:03,590 --> 00:29:04,590
Hard to name

661
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,350
a fair fee.

662
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:09,110
Here's your takeout.

663
00:29:09,510 --> 00:29:10,110
Thanks.

664
00:29:11,680 --> 00:29:12,720
Now I see.

665
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:14,310
You're all talk.

666
00:29:14,590 --> 00:29:16,160
I shouldn't have expected your help.

667
00:29:16,830 --> 00:29:18,160
Don't get upset.

668
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:20,000
Let me analyze it more carefully.

669
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:21,400
Mr. Gao!

670
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:24,030
My interviewee arrived.

671
00:29:24,070 --> 00:29:24,680
Maybe you could

672
00:29:24,790 --> 00:29:25,310
join us.

673
00:29:25,510 --> 00:29:26,270
After I'm done,

674
00:29:26,310 --> 00:29:27,110
I'll analyze

675
00:29:27,110 --> 00:29:27,790
your case.

676
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:28,550
There might be

677
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:29,480
other ways...

678
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:30,550
Go do your thing.

679
00:29:30,880 --> 00:29:31,510
Hope I don't

680
00:29:31,510 --> 00:29:32,110
see you again.

681
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:33,550
You...

682
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:35,350
Well, well.

683
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:46,270
Where were you?

684
00:29:46,960 --> 00:29:48,030
The kitchen's closed.

685
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,640
But we can't skip breakfast.

686
00:29:51,920 --> 00:29:52,880
Cantonese breakfast.

687
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:54,480
Wide selection and delicious.

688
00:29:55,350 --> 00:29:56,920
I just brought some

689
00:29:56,920 --> 00:29:58,110
to Liu and Zhu too.

690
00:29:59,550 --> 00:30:01,030
Looks really good.

691
00:30:01,480 --> 00:30:03,000
Breakfast in the canteen is good too.

692
00:30:03,030 --> 00:30:03,720
But after a year,

693
00:30:03,720 --> 00:30:04,550
I'm sick of it.

694
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:07,110
Wow, Wanzhi.

695
00:30:07,550 --> 00:30:08,160
Let's eat.

696
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,200
You need to get to your train.

697
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,200
After breakfast,

698
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:14,160
you two go pack.

699
00:30:14,310 --> 00:30:15,160
I'm going to Finance.

700
00:30:16,350 --> 00:30:17,510
You still won't give up?

701
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:19,880
For gradates' benefits,

702
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:21,000
my mom spent her days

703
00:30:21,270 --> 00:30:23,110
running between the personnel, health,

704
00:30:23,200 --> 00:30:23,960
and labor bureaus.

705
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,750
For farmers' subsidies,

706
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:27,590
