765
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:12,960
A pregnant lady's making a scene!

766
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:18,030
Shady company!

767
00:32:18,590 --> 00:32:20,400
Give back my money!

768
00:32:21,070 --> 00:32:22,510
Come out!

769
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:24,920
I'll...

770
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:26,070
What are you doing?

771
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,640
Who sent you

772
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:28,480
to sell pesticide?

773
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:29,920
Who's selling pesticide?

774
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:31,880
I'm here to drink it.

775
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,400
Two lives.

776
00:32:33,510 --> 00:32:34,200
Oh no!

777
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:35,310
Who are you?

778
00:32:36,270 --> 00:32:36,750
Qian,

779
00:32:37,030 --> 00:32:38,350
calm down.

780
00:32:38,550 --> 00:32:39,440
How can I calm down?

781
00:32:39,790 --> 00:32:40,880
The five of us

782
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:42,000
cooked for

783
00:32:42,030 --> 00:32:43,070
over 300 people every day.

784
00:32:43,310 --> 00:32:44,440
All that hard work

785
00:32:44,590 --> 00:32:45,960
just for this bonus.

786
00:32:46,550 --> 00:32:48,110
But you broke your word!

787
00:32:48,550 --> 00:32:50,440
My parents are both in the hospital.

788
00:32:50,550 --> 00:32:51,350
If I don't get

789
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:52,510
this money,

790
00:32:53,070 --> 00:32:55,030
I just can't go on anymore!

791
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:56,200
- No!
- Qian!

792
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:57,720
Please calm down!

793
00:32:57,880 --> 00:32:59,110
Director Wang says

794
00:32:59,270 --> 00:33:00,550
he will help us.

795
00:33:10,200 --> 00:33:11,270
I see now.

796
00:33:11,720 --> 00:33:12,750
You three

797
00:33:12,750 --> 00:33:13,720
are in on this together.

798
00:33:14,790 --> 00:33:15,480
Working together

799
00:33:15,640 --> 00:33:16,830
to extort me, huh?

800
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:18,310
Go get security

801
00:33:18,350 --> 00:33:19,160
right now.

802
00:33:20,310 --> 00:33:20,720
What?

803
00:33:21,000 --> 00:33:22,440
Is this how a leader behaves?

804
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:24,000
Pushing people to the edge

805
00:33:24,200 --> 00:33:25,750
rather than keeping a promise?

806
00:33:26,350 --> 00:33:27,590
Listen, girls.

807
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:31,070
You already make plenty.

808
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:32,440
When I came from inland

809
00:33:32,590 --> 00:33:33,640
and saw your pay stubs,

810
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:35,000
my heart trembled.

811
00:33:35,240 --> 00:33:36,880
Are you still not satisfied?

812
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:38,350
If this were inland,

813
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:40,000
only high‑ranking officials

814
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:41,920
would make that much.

815
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:43,790
So you think

816
00:33:43,830 --> 00:33:44,960
we earn too much?

817
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:46,550
Don't you?

818
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:47,790
You're

819
00:33:47,790 --> 00:33:48,960
temporary workers.

820
00:33:49,270 --> 00:33:49,880
No rank,

821
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:50,750
no seniority.

822
00:33:51,030 --> 00:33:52,160
How much more do you want?

823
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:54,030
You're so set

824
00:33:54,110 --> 00:33:55,310
in your old ways!

825
00:33:55,590 --> 00:33:57,200
You wanna equal distribution?

826
00:33:57,510 --> 00:33:58,590
This is the Special Zone!

827
00:33:58,790 --> 00:34:00,270
More work, more pay!

828
00:34:00,480 --> 00:34:01,790
Bonuses for overproduction!

829
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,400
We rest

830
00:34:03,550 --> 00:34:04,880
less than eight hours a day.

831
00:34:05,110 --> 00:34:06,160
Our workload

832
00:34:06,310 --> 00:34:07,880
is double that of other canteens.

833
00:34:08,230 --> 00:34:09,630
Our food quality

834
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:11,800
always ranks first.

835
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:13,400
The bonus

836
00:34:13,550 --> 00:34:14,190
is 50%

837
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:15,360
of our salary.

838
00:34:15,510 --> 00:34:17,630
The leadership said it!

839
00:34:18,110 --> 00:34:19,000
It must be honored!

840
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:20,920
Or we'll keep fighting!

841
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:21,440
Yes!

842
00:34:21,590 --> 00:34:23,030
We'll fight to the end!

843
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:24,000
No! Hurry!

844
00:34:24,550 --> 00:34:25,190
Come on, Qian!

845
00:34:25,190 --> 00:34:25,840
Qian!

846
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:26,670
Security department!

847
00:34:27,230 --> 00:34:28,320
Put down the pesticide!

848
00:34:28,550 --> 00:34:29,630
Let's talk nicely.

849
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:31,150
Talk nicely? No way!

850
00:34:31,150 --> 00:34:32,960
Have you ever talked nicely with me?

851
00:34:33,150 --> 00:34:34,190
I can't go on!

852
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:36,360
Qian!

853
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:38,110
No! Stop it!

854
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:44,550
Mr. Hu,

855
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:45,400
see.

856
00:34:52,550 --> 00:34:53,110
What's up?

857
00:34:53,550 --> 00:34:54,230
Li Juan,

858
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:55,630
what's she doing?

859
00:34:56,070 --> 00:34:56,710
Mr. Hu,

860
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,070
didn't you

861
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,030
already leave?

862
00:34:59,320 --> 00:35:00,110
I was about to.

863
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,320
But Mr. Gao invited me

864
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:03,880
to give a class.

865
00:35:04,070 --> 00:35:04,630
And today,

866
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:05,670
at the station,

867
00:35:05,710 --> 00:35:06,510
he stopped me

868
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:07,920
and said you were suing us.

869
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:10,400
Yes, we're suing.

870
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:11,590
Suing him.

871
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:13,070
No, Mr. Hu.

872
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:15,030
This has nothing to do with me.

873
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,550
I've been following the rules.

874
00:35:17,070 --> 00:35:18,550
No matter how unreasonable they are,

875
00:35:18,880 --> 00:35:20,000
I won't give in.

876
00:35:22,360 --> 00:35:22,800
Well,

877
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:23,920
clear the area.

878
00:35:25,670 --> 00:35:26,070
Wang,

879
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:27,510
Fang Wanzhi,

880
00:35:28,590 --> 00:35:29,190
come with me.

881
00:35:34,070 --> 00:35:35,000
I briefed you on this

882
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,190
before I left, right?

883
00:35:36,710 --> 00:35:37,590
Yes, you did.

884
00:35:38,670 --> 00:35:39,920
But there's no contract.

885
00:35:40,550 --> 00:35:41,840
That was our oversight.

886
00:35:42,230 --> 00:35:42,880
Sure,

887
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:44,480
Liu isn't

888
00:35:44,710 --> 00:35:45,400
well-educated

889
00:35:46,070 --> 00:35:47,150
and not big on contracts.

890
00:35:47,510 --> 00:35:49,030
But anyway, their workload

891
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:50,710
went up

892
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:52,400
to meet the site's needs,

893
00:35:52,670 --> 00:35:54,190
so we added a year-end bonus.

894
00:35:54,960 --> 00:35:56,000
This was discussed

895
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:56,920
at our meeting.

896
00:35:58,670 --> 00:35:59,710
You discussed it?

897
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:01,960
But, Mr. Hu,

898
00:36:02,480 --> 00:36:03,150
do you know

899
00:36:03,190 --> 00:36:04,230
